name: FREE Token
description: Freeper is a social2earn Dapp built on BNB Chain, integrating DID community, live streaming,chatting and a NFT marketplace. Everyone can issue social NFTs on freeper and automatically create a chatting group. Users can participate in the Ladder Tournament System (LTS) ranking to get more rights and rewards by collecting Freeper officially certified Core Fan NFTs (CFN) and synthesize Socialite PASS. Another fun feature is called Bounty Live, where the anchors and their NFT holders can enjoy the earnings of each live broadcast, and all the audiences can watch live to earn. Freeper App also supports multi-token payment, which provides various project tokens with an use scenary and help burn them..
